Package: ukfloodr
Type: Package
Title: Download Data on Real Time Flood-Monitoring in the UK
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Downloads data from the UK Environment Agency flood-monitoring API,
    <https://environment.data.gov.uk/flood-monitoring/doc/reference>. The 
    Environment Agency flood-monitoring API provides developers with access to 
    near real time information covering flood warnings and flood alerts, flood 
    areas which to which warnings or alerts apply, measurements of water levels 
    and flows, and information on the monitoring stations providing those 
    measurements.
